unison-lua
==========

This crate is a fork of lua-src-rs by Aleksandr Orlenko (khvzak):
    https://github.com/khvzak/lua-src-rs

Modifications by Unison 2D:
  - Added wasm32-unknown-unknown build support using LLVM clang and a
    bundled libc sysroot (wasm-sysroot/include/).
  - Trimmed to Lua 5.4 only; removed lua-5.1.5 / lua-5.2.4 / lua-5.3.6
    source trees and corresponding dispatch in src/lib.rs.
  - Preserved [package] name = "lua-src" and [lib] name = "lua_src" so
    the crate remains ABI-compatible with mlua-sys's `use lua_src::...`
    imports when substituted via [patch.crates-io]. Unison branding
    lives in the crate directory (crates/unison-lua/), README, and
    NOTICE — Cargo's patch machinery resolves by package name, so the
    published name stays `lua-src`.

